00:08:51.885 --> 00:08:52.599
That makes sense.

00:08:52.599 --> 00:08:53.803
Nobel gases, they are gases.

00:08:53.803 --> 00:08:55.104
They don't, they're not very reactive.

00:08:55.104 --> 00:08:57.240
they don't bond so they don't form

00:08:57.240 --> 00:08:58.783
kind of a structure that can even do

00:08:58.783 --> 00:09:00.155
